---
title: Middle Eastern Chickpeas & Jacket Potatoes with Garden Salad & Garlic Yoghurt
description: These potatoes are dressed to impress, so let’s be swept off our feet with these golden jacket potatoes with a saucy
Middle Eastern chickpea toss underneath. It’s sure to be a real stunner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/middle-eastern-chickpeas-jacket-potatoes-985c8bb7.jpg
